00:01:26,916 --> 00:01:29,083
each representing a different kind of temptation

37
00:01:29,083 --> 00:01:31,166
that humans just can't seem to resist

38
00:01:31,791 --> 00:01:34,416
their names Tanhā craving

39
00:01:34,666 --> 00:01:36,125
Arati boredom

40
